kcast (0.2.7-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed install(DIRECTORY package/...) shipping raw C++ source/CMakeLists
    as installed plasmoid data.
  * Fixed panel-icon scroll-to-change-volume, dead cursor styling, and a
    non-existent scanDevicesWithCatt() call in Settings' device search.
  * Fixed the bridge's mediaUrl going stale after a drag-and-drop or
    file-picker selection.
  * Now also builds and releases RPMs via OBS (previously .deb only).

